OL,4,Cjailed for life
OL,6,FA man who left his victim in a bathtub
OL,7,Fafter murdering him has been jailed
OL,8,Ffor life.
OL,10,FMarvin James, 40, was found dead by
OL,11,FMetropolitan Police officers in his
OL,12,FHaringey flat in September, 2024,
OL,13,Fafter neighbours raised concerns over
OL,14,Fa foul smell.
OL,16,FDante Forrest, 36, of Moselle Avenue
OL,17,Fin Haringey, appeared at the Old
OL,18,FBailey on Tuesday and was sentenced to
OL,19,Fa minimum term of 22 years.
