OL,3,CKiller who left victim in a bathtub
OL,4,Cjailed for life
OL,6,FIt follows his murder conviction on
OL,7,FThursday 14 November.
OL,9,FMetropolitan Police detectives linked
OL,10,Fhim to the killing through forensic
OL,11,Fevidence and extensive CCTV analysis.
OL,13,FOfficers were called to Marvin James'
OL,14,Fflat last year, and found the property
OL,15,Fboarded up, padlocked and in complete
OL,16,Fdarkness.
OL,18,FAfter forcing entry, officers found
OL,19,Fhis body in the bathtub. He is
OL,20,Fbelieved to have been dead for around
OL,21,F10 days.
