OL,4,Cjailed for life
OL,6,FA post-mortem examination revealed
OL,7,Ffractures to Marvin's head and face,
OL,8,Falong with multiple stab wounds. There
OL,9,Fwere no signs of forced entry, which
OL,10,Fthe police said suggested that the
OL,11,Fattacker had access to the property
OL,12,Fand attempted to cover their tracks.
OL,14,FDetectives reviewed hundreds of hours
OL,15,Fof CCTV. Footage showed Marvin with
OL,16,FDante Forrest ten days before his body
OL,17,Fwas discovered, with Marvin seen
OL,18,Fcollecting a pizza - the last time he
OL,19,Fwas seen alive.
