OL,6,FBlood stains were later found on the
OL,7,Fpizza box and a shirt inside the flat,
OL,8,Fproviding a key forensic links to
OL,9,FForrest.
OL,11,FFurther CCTV, filmed on Thursday, 19
OL,12,FSeptember 2024, captured Forrest
OL,13,Fwearing distinctive purple, blue and
OL,14,Fwhite trainers. These were the same
OL,15,Fpair Marvin had been wearing when last
OL,16,Fseen.
OL,18,FThe trainers have never been recovered.
