OL,11,FForrest was arrested and charged with
OL,12,Fmurder on Wednesday 25 September 2024.
OL,14,FIn a statement, Marvin's family
OL,15,Fthanked everyone involved in the
OL,16,Finvestigation and said that while
OL,17,Fjustice had been delivered, no verdict
OL,18,Fcould ease their loss.
OL,20,FThey said Marvin would "forever be
OL,21,Floved, missed, and remembered."
